apcom\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|92\n|''[[NFL GameDay (video game series)#NFL GameDay 99|NFL GameDay 99]]''\n|[[989 Studios]]\n|[[Sony Computer Entertainment]]\n|{{dts|1998-07-31}}\n|1,120,000\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"usplatinum\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|93\n|''[[Arc the Lad (video game)|Arc the Lad]]''\n|[[G-Craft]]<br/>Winds\n|[[Sony Computer Entertainment]]\n|{{dts|1995-06-30}}\n|1,100,000\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"jpplatinum\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|94\n|''[[Devil Dice]]''\n|[[Shift (company)|Shift]]\n|[[Sony Computer Entertainment]]<br/>[[THQ]]\n|{{dts|1998-06-18}}\n|1,100,000\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"jpplatinum\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|95\n|''[[beatmania]]''\n|[[Konami]]\n|[[Konami]]\n|{{dts|1998-10-01}}\n|1,100,000\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"jpplatinum\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|96\n|''[[Derby Stallion|Derby Stallion 99]]''\n|ParityBit\n|[[ASCII Corporation]]\n|{{dts|1999-09-30}}\n|1,100,000\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"jpplatinum\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|97\n|''[[Star Ocean: The Second Story]]''\n|[[tri-Ace]]\n|[[Enix]]<br/>[[Sony Computer Entertainment]]\n|{{dts|1998-07-30}}\n|1,094,000\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"starocean\">{{cite web |url=http://www.tri-ace.co.jp//company/sales.html |title=2005\u5e749\u6708\u73fe\u5728\u306e\u4e3b\u306a\u958b\u767a\u30bf\u30a4\u30c8\u30eb\u306e\u8ca9\u58f2\u5b9f\u7e3e\u3002 |publisher=[[tri-Ace]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=May 2, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080916225226/http://www.tri-ace.co.jp/company/sales.html |archive-date=September 16, 2008 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|98\n|''[[Ace Combat 2]]''\n|[[Namco]]\n|[[Namco]]\n|{{dts|1997-05-30}}\n|1,092,000\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"AceCombat\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|99\n|''[[2Xtreme]]'